rpg.v4.server.state
Interface State

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractState, IntegerAbilityState, IntegerState, StringListState, StringState
public interface State

Maintains a set of modifiers or string based entity states from a variety of sources.

A state should be Observable so that they can be added later. When a change is comitted in a staterecord, it recalculates and notifies the observers.
